## 🔴 ABSOLUTE RULES (FOLLOW THESE RELIGIOUSLY)

### Rule 1: TypeScript Strict - NEVER BREAK
- NO `any` type ever
- ALL functions must have return types
- ALL props must be interfaces/types
- Run `npm run type-check` before every commit
- If it doesn't compile with strict mode, it doesn't go in

### Rule 2: Reusable Components ALWAYS
- Check `src/components/ui/` before creating anything new
- 25+ components already exist - USE THEM
- Never duplicate HTML/CSS
- If new component needed, make it generic and reusable
- Export via `src/components/ui/index.ts` (barrel export)

### Rule 3: Tailwind Classes ONLY - NO INLINE STYLES
- Use Tailwind classes exclusively
- No `style={{}}` attributes
- No CSS modules
- No styled-components
- Use design system colors: bg-pink-600, text-purple-700, etc.

### Rule 4: Import from index.ts ALWAYS
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT
import { Button, Card, Input } from '@/components/ui';

// ❌ WRONG
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
```

### Rule 5: Clear Names - NO ABBREVIATIONS
- `isUserLoggedIn` not `isUserLI`
- `handleButtonClick` not `handleBC`
- `getUserProfile` not `getUP`
- Variable names should be self-documenting

### Rule 6: PWA Always Functional - NEVER BREAK
- Service Worker must be registered
- Manifest must be valid
- Icons must exist (192x192, 512x512)
- Install prompt must work
- Test in Chrome DevTools → Application tab

### Rule 7: Types EVERYWHERE
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT
interface UserProps {
  name: string;
  age: number;
  onSubmit: (data: User) => Promise<void>;
}

// ❌ WRONG
function User(props) {}
```

### Rule 8: NO console.log in Production Code
- Use only in development
- Remove before pushing
- Use logger for production

### Rule 9: Semantic Commits ALWAYS
```
feat:       New feature
fix:        Bug fix
chore:      Dependencies, setup
refactor:   Code reorganization
test:       Tests
docs:       Documentation
```

### Rule 10: Test Before Push ALWAYS
```bash
npm run type-check    # Must pass
npm run build         # Must compile
npm run dev          # Must run without errors
```

## 📱 PWA REQUIREMENTS (MANDATORY)
- Installable on all browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari)
- Works offline with Service Worker
- Push notifications ready
- Background sync ready
- Responsive on all screen sizes

## 🔐 AUTHENTICATION & SECURITY
- Supabase Auth with email/password
- JWT automatically in headers
- Row Level Security (RLS) for database
- No sensitive data in localStorage
- Environment variables for secrets

## 📊 28 PAGES (STRUCTURE)
**Public Pages** (no login):
- `/` (landing)
- `/login` (authentication)
- `/cadastro` (registration)
- `/perfil-publico/:slug` (professional profile)
- `/agendar/:slug` (public booking)
- `/precos` (pricing)
- `/contato` (contact)
- `/recursos` (features)

**Authenticated Pages** (20 more):
- `/dashboard` (KPIs)
- `/app` (scheduler calendar)
- `/clientes` (CRM)
- `/servicos` (services management)
- `/horarios` (hours configuration)
- `/pagamentos` (payments/invoicing)
- `/notificacoes` (notifications center)
- `/portfolio` (work gallery)
- `/perfil-profissional` (profile editor)
- `/personalizacao` (theme customization)
- `/google-calendar` (Google integration)
- `/whatsapp` (WhatsApp integration)
- `/transacoes` (transaction history)
- `/onboarding` (welcome tutorial)
- ... (6 more)

## 🚀 WHEN STARTING DEVELOPMENT
1. Read `docs/MEMORIA.md` (project context)
2. Read `docs/REGRAS.md` (mandatory rules)
3. Read `docs/ESPECIFICACOES.md` (full specs)
4. Check `docs/GUIA_ARQUIVOS.md` (where files go)
5. Run `npm run dev` to start
6. All new pages go in `src/routes/`
7. All new components go in `src/components/ui/`
8. Export everything via `index.ts`
9. Always use Tailwind + TypeScript

## 🐳 DOCKER (READY TO USE)
```bash
# Development with hot reload
docker-compose up dev

# Production optimized
docker-compose up prod

# Build image
docker build -t suaagenda:latest .
```

## 📋 FILE PLACEMENT REFERENCE
| What | Where | Example |
|------|-------|---------|
| Page (from Lovable) | `src/routes/` | `src/routes/dashboard.tsx` |
| Reusable Component | `src/components/ui/` | `src/components/ui/card.tsx` |
| Layout Component | `src/components/layout/` | `src/components/layout/header.tsx` |
| Custom Hook | `src/hooks/` | `src/hooks/useAuth.ts` |
| Type Definition | `src/types/` | `src/types/user.ts` |
| Utility Function | `src/lib/` | `src/lib/formatDate.ts` |
| External Integration | `src/integrations/` | `src/integrations/supabase.ts` |

